ygData.messageBody:
UH.....

Duh. There I go again..blur as always..i still can't identify some email
handles with
the EQ names.. .

Tri,
Good luck on your attachment..hope you meet some babes there...maybe those
High Elf types? LOL
Or if u prefer 'bigger' type then hope for some barbarian lady hehehe.
We're all gonna miss your sow but hey when you're back maybe we can hunt
together to lvl you
up quick to get Spirit of Cheetah!!! Wooooo...now that's one that makes me
drool after trying
out Sereph's Accelendo something bard song. Once again, Hope to see you
soon!

FF,
If you read the previous one,,sorry hor..got mistaken..but hey..since i
already said it..next time you
go attachment or anything..i don't need to say liao k? LOL Joking...

Sereph,

Thanks for telling me man! Uh..lady! uh..oh well...

Everyone,

BTW...anyone who needs fine steel weapons for their alternate chars or
something...
check out the hermit living in South Karana. He's dropped FS Long sword, FS
Short sword,
FS 2 handed Sword before. They're expensive at npcs right if u try to buy
them? Was thinking of selling
them to PCs but i think those damned ppl nowadays all twinked..who even
wants them man? Unless
i can find good low lvl chars to sell to in maybe more newbie
territory..i'll just sell to NPC loh..no choice.
Any ideas? Need cash as always...sigh... BTW..that hermit is lvl 20 FYI.

Zanderion Magi of the 6th Rank
